  <summary date="2017-03-15T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Jessie's Law

This bill requires the Department of Health and Human Services to develop and disseminate standards for hospitals and physicians regarding displaying the history of opioid addiction in the medical records of patients who have provided information about their addiction to a health care provider.</summary>
